sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>5000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant EvalJob as Evaluation Job Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference<br/>Endpoint (KServe/vLLM)

    Note over Client,Model: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Submission and Execution

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (when configured)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authentication result
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(namespace from X-Tenant header)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authorization result

    EvalHub->>PostgreSQL: Persist evaluation job<br/>TLS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Connection string
    EvalHub->>MLflow: Create experiment<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    MLflow-->>EvalHub: Experiment ID

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap + Job<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created

    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (Job ID)

    Note over EvalJob,S3: Init Container: Download test data
    K8sAPI->>EvalJob: Schedule Pod
    EvalJob->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>EvalJob: Test data artifacts

    Note over EvalJob,Model: Adapter: Run evaluation benchmarks
    EvalJob->>Model: Inference requests<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (from model auth secret)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Model-->>EvalJob: Inference responses

    EvalJob->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Status updates
    EvalJob->>MLflow: Log run results<br/>Auth: SA Token (projected volume)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (service CA)
    MLflow-->>EvalJob: Run logged

    Note over Client,Model: Flow 2: Multi-Tenant Authorization

    Client->>EvalHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + X-Tenant header
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (2min cache TTL)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: User identity
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(5min allow / 30s deny cache)<br/>namespace = X-Tenant value
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authorized (namespace-scoped)
    EvalHub->>PostgreSQL: Query jobs for tenant
    PostgreSQL-->>EvalHub: Tenant-scoped results
    EvalHub-->>Client: 200 OK (filtered results)
